Package: gglinedensity
Title: Make DenseLines Heatmaps with 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Create a raster plot of line density using a 'ggplot2' statistic
    implementing the DenseLines algorithm, which
    "normalizes time series by the arc length to compute accurate densities"
    (Moritz and Fisher, 2018) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.1808.06019>.
